    IN UINT8 Len[],
    OUT UINT16 Code[]
)
/*++

Routine Description:
Assign code to each symbol based on the code length array
Arguments:
n - number of symbols
Len - the code length array
Code - stores codes for each symbol
Returns: (VOID)
